data.description: Get your beach feel right here in Victoria! Enjoy every bit of your summers in Texas in your backyard paradise sliding in and cooling down in your in-ground pool. This 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom spacious home is located in the sought after Terra Vista subdivision close to restaurants and shopping. Open concept gives you a view of your outdoor oasis from the kitchen and living spaces and the home boasts window blinds and granite counters throughout. There is a second space to use as your formal dining, office, second living space, gaming space, the possibilities are endless! 2 car garage with entry to your own laundry room. Primary suite includes a double vanity, large walk-in shower and walk-in closet. Enjoy all the neighborhood amenities of a playground across the street, basketball courts, and sidewalks for some extra time outside. Book your showing today!
